item.title: SoftLayer_Event_Log
item.description: SoftLayer_Event_Log Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Event_Log data type contains an event detail occurred upon various SoftLayer resources. Local accountId Account id with which the event is associated Type: integer eventCreateDate Event creation date in millisecond precision Type: dateTime eventName Event name such as "reboot", "cancel", "update host" and so on. Type: string ipAddress The remote IP Address that made the request Type: string
